# packages/server/.dockerignore — mirrors the root .dockerignore for the case
# where a build is run with `packages/server/` as the context. Today the
# Dockerfile expects the monorepo root as the context (see comment at the top
# of `Dockerfile`); this file is here as defense-in-depth.

**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo

**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes

**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/.idea
**/.vscode

**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

**/.vercel

**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

**/README.md
**/CHANGELOG.md

**/Dockerfile
**/.dockerignore
